        <updateDate>2013-11-22T19:54:34Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>International Hydrocephalus Treatment and Training Act - Amends the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 to authorize the President to provide assistance to support a network of trained medical practitioners to treat hydrocephalus in children at pediatric hospitals and hydrocephalus treatment centers in developing countries.</p> <p>Requires such assistance to provide for surgeon training and establishment of at least 20 treatment centers.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>International Hydrocephalus Treatment and Training Act</title>
    <titles>
      <item>
